title: Oak Street Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Menu changes daily and includes a wide choice of vegan and gluten free dishes. Ranging from always vegan soups and mainly vegan stews, to out of the ordinary salads (2 out of 3 will always be vegan), some vegan toasties & a plentiful selection of vegan cakes and pastries (sweet and savory). All food is made-in-house.
streetAddress: 17 Oak St, Manchester Craft and Design Centre
